fluorescent protein properties from fpbase

Source: R/data.R
fpbase_data.Rd

A dataset containing some of the properties of all the 'basic' (single fluorescent state) fluorescent proteins in the fpbase database (downloaded 2022.10.04).

fpbase_data

Format

A data frame with 593 rows and 16 variables:

url

FPbase url

name

name

stokes

Stokes shift (nm)

slug

slug - lower case name used in url

ipg_id

Identical Protein Group ID at Pubmed

agg

oligomerisation state

ex_max

wavelength of excitation peak (nm)

em_max

wavelength of emission peak (nm)

ext_coeff

excitation coefficient (EC, M-1cm-1)

qy

quantum yield

pka

pKa

brightness

brightness

bleach

rate of photobleaching/photostability (s)

maturation

maturation half time (min)

lifetime

fluorescence lifetime (ns)

cofactor

cofactor required for fluorescence (if any)

Source

https://www.fpbase.org/api/proteins/basic/?format=json
